{"tid":991772,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今日再嗌快餐外賣FXXD熊貓 疑似俾人食過","createTime":"2019-01-22T15:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T04:28:59.000Z","uid":232607,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0978f659466e394b52f072c8f9cba6ef86475f52","tid":991772,"uid":232607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"事緣係我成日嗌依間快餐外賣<br />\n因為我住嗰區 所以嗌親都係啲香港人送黎<br />\n而我嗌過兩次一間食咖喱嘅餐廳都會係同一個印度籍人士送 佢送親過嚟都要個幾鐘<br />\n我自己去買都係半個鐘 但我真係懶得行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我兩次都係嗌兩盒飯 都係有一盒嘅膠紙俾人開過 同咖喱少咗一半<br />\n我唔排除係佢食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Xna17L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Xna17L.png&h=ae199849&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p8Us4k7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp8Us4k7.png&h=6c084f70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8ba60c615ded67c9455cd2b1479e29e2e1e8eea","tid":991772,"uid":126697,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"見過有蝻車手開黎食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢見到"},{"pid":"6516465f82159ea17c54386b0abc2f6309f5c952","tid":991772,"uid":88491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩，係我見到即刻唔敢食<br />\n點知佢有無病，仲可能直接用手乸"},{"pid":"c7674d4fb6ed64346b4e53cc19773d9986f56ce0","tid":991772,"uid":77461,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"食咖哩唔食飯 仲要用手食 即係玩鳩自己"},{"pid":"5807e203e51982422310802d619f5fc49d50ad41","tid":991772,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"似倒瀉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d277c3e8a34ec81fbf075a5a1b25ce49